Package net.sourceforge.JDash.logger

Class Summary
DatabaseLogger This class is the DAO for all database logging activity Whant to read and/or write parameter values to a database, then use this DAO.
DataLogger This is the interface needed to implement in order for a class to be a logger.
LoggerExporter This class gets linked to a monitor in order to export to a CSV, all the ecu values.
LoggerPlaybackMonitor This monitor is a completely different animal.
LogParameter This extension to a Parameter used by the logging packing contains the extra needed methods for logging use.
PlaybackControlDialog This dialog class is a modless dialog box that will pop giving the user control over the playback logger.
